      "text": "Across **South Florida** and the ** Tri-State area (New York & Connecticut)**, more people are rethinking how they care for their clothes. Eco-friendly dry cleaning is no longer just a niche service — it’s becoming the new standard for residents who value health, quality, and sustainability. But what’s driving the shift, and why do these regions in particular stand out?"
